==晚年==
1906年至1915間，柏基特在新英格蘭聯盟的球隊執教，並打了幾場比賽。<ref name="minors">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=burket001jes|title=Jesse Burkett Minor League Statistics & History|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=February 1, 2013|archive-date=2015-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150611095314/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/player.cgi?id=burket001jes|dead-url=no}}</ref>他還在1906年成為球隊的打擊王。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/leader.cgi?type=bat&id=69d28ad9|title=1906 New England League Batting Leaders|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=February 1, 2013|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613011651/http://www.baseball-reference.com/minors/leader.cgi?type=bat&id=69d28ad9|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1916年，柏基特從棒球界退休。並在年底於一間銅器工廠工作，<ref name=Day2>{{cite news|title=Jesse Burkett now factory employee|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1915&dat=19161208&id=W_0gAAAAIBAJ&pg=6651,4060589|access-date=January 2, 2015|work=[[The_Day_(New_London)|The Day]]|date=December 8, 1916|archive-date=2022-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110032213/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1915&dat=19161208&id=W_0gAAAAIBAJ&pg=6651%2C4060589|dead-url=no}}</ref>不過他還同時擔任大學棒球隊的教練。<ref name=Day>{{cite news|title=Jesse Burkett to pilot Holy Cross|url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1915&dat=19161223&id=aP0gAAAAIBAJ&pg=3901,5820942|access-date=January 2, 2015|work=[[The_Day_(New_London)|The Day]]|date=December 23, 1916|archive-date=2022-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220110033808/https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1915&dat=19161223&id=aP0gAAAAIBAJ&pg=3901%2C5820942|dead-url=no}}</ref>

日後，柏基特一路擔任小聯盟球隊教練到1933年止。<ref name="minors"/>他在1946年入選名人堂，成為第一位獲得此殊榮的西維吉尼亞州人。<ref name="statistics">{{cite web|url=https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/b/burkeje01.shtml|title=Jesse Burkett Statistics and History|work=[[Baseball-Reference.com|Baseball-Reference.com]]|access-date=February 1, 2013|archive-date=2021-06-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210616180017/https://www.baseball-reference.com/players/b/burkeje01.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

1953年5月27日，柏基特因病去世，享年84歲。<ref name="statistics"/>
